name: Be Mine
description:
Love Potion no. 14
“ Be Mine “
A box of chocolate might change your heart,
A various bitter and sweet delish will amuse your taste bud. 
This one is the most powerful love potion ever.
Made in a form of luscious sweets, your lover will not suspicious at once. But be careful ! A long term comsumption might led to an overdose by love state.
Be wise and be gentle. Do not rush love, dear ✨
